data.description: Price improvement on this custom home that sits on a large tree lined lot. New carpet and paint upstairs just completed in December 2023. Home has a large master bedroom with its own deck. Two large family rooms for entertainment or just having family around. Downstairs has a kitchenette, sauna and a three-bedroom dorm, bathroom has a separate tub and shower and office. The backyard has several fruit trees. large pines and aspens that will have you believing you are in a mountain paradise. So much so that there have been many deer known to come and visit.
